---
import DefaultLayout from '@layouts/DefaultLayout.astro'
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components'
import { Avatar, AvatarGroup } from 'accessible-astro-components'
---

<DefaultLayout title="About Riley Skipper - Web Developer">
  <section class="my-24">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-16 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-8">
          <h1 class="text-6xl lg:text-8xl">About Me</h1>
          <p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl">
            I'm Riley Skipper, a Web Developer and UX/UI Researcher who believes that great websites should be accessible to everyone. 
            I combine modern development practices with a deep commitment to inclusive design and user experience.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 min-[500px]:flex-row">
            <a class="button has-icon" href="/portfolio/">
              <Icon name="lucide:briefcase" />
              View My Work
            </a>
            <a class="button has-icon color-secondary" href="/contact">
              <Icon name="lucide:mail" />
              Get in Touch
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
          <Image 
            class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl" 
            src="/astronaut-hero-img.webp" 
            alt="Riley Skipper - Web Developer" 
            width={500} 
            height={500} 
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="my-64">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="mb-16 text-6xl">My Story</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <p class="text-xl">
            My journey in web development began at Camden County College where I earned my Web Design A.A.S. 
            This foundation led me to Arizona State University where I completed my Internet & Web Development B.S., 
            solidifying my passion for creating digital experiences that make a real difference.
          </p>
          <p class="text-xl">
            I discovered early on that accessibility wasn't just a nice-to-have—it was essential. 
            Working with legal associations and university systems taught me that every user matters, 
            and every website should work for everyone, regardless of their abilities.
          </p>
          <p class="text-xl">
            Today, I specialize in building websites that are not only beautiful and functional 
            but also inclusive and accessible to everyone. My experience with Drupal, WordPress, 
            and modern web technologies allows me to create solutions that truly serve their users.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-100 to-secondary-100 p-8 dark:from-primary-900 dark:to-secondary-900">
            <h3 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold">My Mission</h3>
            <p class="text-lg">
              "Strive not to be a success, but rather to be of value." - Albert Einstein
              I create web experiences that are accessible, performant, and valuable to all users. 
              I believe that technology should bring people together, not create barriers.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary-100 to-primary-100 p-8 dark:from-secondary-900 dark:to-primary-900">
            <h3 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold">My Values</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-lg">
              <li>• Accessibility first in everything I build</li>
              <li>• User-centered design and research</li>
              <li>• Clean, maintainable code that scales</li>
              <li>• Continuous learning and growth</li>
              <li>• Collaborative problem-solving</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="my-64">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="mb-16 text-6xl">Experience & Education</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <h3 class="mb-8 text-3xl">Professional Experience</h3>
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <div class="border-l-4 border-primary pl-6">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold">Web Developer</h4>
              <p class="text-lg text-muted">Rutgers University • May 2022 - Current</p>
              <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm">
                <li>• Designing and deploying dynamic elements and page layouts using Drupal CMS</li>
                <li>• Prototyping and responsive designing websites and products for end users</li>
                <li>• Accessibility management to comply with standards of ADA requirements</li>
                <li>• Maintenance through diagnosing and resolving bugs, and QA testing within a local server environment</li>
                <li>• Establishing a cohesive flow and branding by creating templates for users' editing and design needs</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="border-l-4 border-secondary pl-6">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold">Junior Web Developer</h4>
              <p class="text-lg text-muted">Legal Associations Management • Aug 2021 - May 2022</p>
              <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm">
                <li>• WordPress based developing and maintaining law firm associations around the U.S.</li>
                <li>• Assisting in setting up algorithms and data structures using WordPress' Oxygen and jQuery</li>
                <li>• Designing mockups and prototyping with Figma, and key member to check for QA</li>
                <li>• Collaboration with clients and marketing to establish design needs</li>
                <li>• Monthly SEO management and improvements using tools such as Moz Pro and Alexa</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="border-l-4 border-accent pl-6">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold">UX/UI Intern</h4>
              <p class="text-lg text-muted">Philadelphia Printworks • Apr 2019 - Oct 2019</p>
              <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm">
                <li>• User experience research by monitoring interaction trends</li>
                <li>• Editing copy for upcoming social media posts</li>
                <li>• Creative thinking allowing for brainstorming new avenues to increase user engagement</li>
                <li>• Identifying design and code issues and reaching solutions for optimal user satisfaction</li>
                <li>• Collaborative redesign of web navigation for improved UX</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="mb-8 text-3xl">Education & Certifications</h3>
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-card p-6">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold">Internet & Web Development B.S.</h4>
              <p class="text-lg text-muted">Arizona State University • 2017-2019</p>
              <p class="mt-2">Comprehensive study of web development, user experience design, and modern web technologies.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-card p-6">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold">Web Design A.A.S.</h4>
              <p class="text-lg text-muted">Camden County College • 2015-2017</p>
              <p class="mt-2">Foundation in web design principles, HTML, CSS, and fundamental development practices.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-card p-6">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold">ADA Compliance Experience</h4>
              <p class="text-lg text-muted">Rutgers University</p>
              <p class="mt-2">Extensive experience implementing and maintaining accessibility standards in higher education environments.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="my-64">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="mb-16 text-6xl">Skills & Technologies</h2>
      <div class="space-y-12">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-card p-6">
            <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold">Content Management</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li>• Drupal 9 & 10</li>
              <li>• WordPress</li>
              <li>• Oxygen Builder</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-card p-6">
            <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold">Frontend Development</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li>• HTML 5</li>
              <li>• CSS</li>
              <li>• JavaScript</li>
              <li>• Bootstrap 4 & 5</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-card p-6">
            <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold">Backend & Tools</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li>• MySQL</li>
              <li>• Apache</li>
              <li>• Lando/Docker</li>
              <li>• XAMPP</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-card p-6">
            <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold">Development Tools</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li>• GitHub</li>
              <li>• PHPMyAdmin</li>
              <li>• jQuery</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-card p-6">
            <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold">Design & UX</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li>• Figma</li>
              <li>• Adobe Creative Cloud</li>
              <li>• Wireframing</li>
              <li>• Prototyping</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-card p-6">
            <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold">Research & Testing</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li>• User Testing</li>
              <li>• Collaborative Design</li>
              <li>• SEO Management</li>
              <li>• QA Testing</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="my-64">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="mb-16 text-6xl">When I'm Not Coding</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-card p-6">
          <Icon name="lucide:users" class="mb-4 h-12 w-12 text-primary" />
          <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold">Team Leadership</h3>
          <p>Drawing from my experience as a Barista Trainer at Starbucks, I excel at leading teams and creating positive, collaborative environments.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-card p-6">
          <Icon name="lucide:search" class="mb-4 h-12 w-12 text-secondary" />
          <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold">User Research</h3>
          <p>I love diving deep into user behavior and interaction patterns to create better digital experiences.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-card p-6">
          <Icon name="lucide:heart" class="mb-4 h-12 w-12 text-accent" />
          <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold">Problem Solving</h3>
          <p>I enjoy identifying design and code issues and finding creative solutions for optimal user satisfaction.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-card p-6">
          <Icon name="lucide:message-circle" class="mb-4 h-12 w-12 text-primary" />
          <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold">Client Collaboration</h3>
          <p>I thrive on working directly with clients and marketing teams to establish design needs and goals.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-card p-6">
          <Icon name="lucide:trending-up" class="mb-4 h-12 w-12 text-secondary" />
          <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold">SEO & Analytics</h3>
          <p>I'm passionate about improving website performance and visibility through SEO management and analytics.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-card p-6">
          <Icon name="lucide:accessibility" class="mb-4 h-12 w-12 text-accent" />
          <h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold">Accessibility Advocacy</h3>
          <p>I'm committed to ensuring digital experiences are accessible to everyone, regardless of ability.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="my-64">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="mb-16 text-6xl">Let's Work Together</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <p class="text-xl">
            I'm always excited to take on new projects that challenge me to grow and create something meaningful. 
            Whether you need a new website, want to improve accessibility, or just want to chat about web development, 
            I'd love to hear from you.
          </p>
          <p class="text-xl">
            I believe in building long-term relationships with clients, not just completing projects. 
            I want to understand your goals, your users, and your vision so we can create something truly special together.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 min-[500px]:flex-row">
            <a class="button has-icon" href="/contact">
              <Icon name="lucide:mail" />
              Start a Project
            </a>
            <a class="button has-icon color-secondary" href="/portfolio/">
              <Icon name="lucide:eye" />
              See My Work
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-100 to-secondary-100 p-8 dark:from-primary-900 dark:to-secondary-900">
          <h3 class="mb-6 text-2xl font-bold">What I'm Looking For</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-lg">
            <li>• Projects that make a positive impact</li>
            <li>• Opportunities to push accessibility boundaries</li>
            <li>• Long-term partnerships with great clients</li>
            <li>• Projects that challenge me to learn and grow</li>
            <li>• Work that aligns with my values</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</DefaultLayout> 